{"tid":2261262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打：7成外資企業考慮將產能移出中国","createTime":"2020-10-28T07:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T08:40:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6bae798304600c51e7d274565a25cff539dc5356","tid":2261262,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"渣打集團最近針對中國大灣區進行調查，受到美中關係緊張及疫情影響，有高達7成左右企業考慮將產能全部或部分移出中國，以分散供應鏈的風險。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，渣打集團2020年度大灣區調查結果，更積極考慮移轉產能的企業43%，另有25%則是考慮遷廠，等於約68%企業正考慮將產能移出中國，渣打觀察，這主要是以往過度集中單一市場的供應鏈策略，受到疫情考驗，顯示已無法因應快速變遷的全球環境，企業必須重新檢視供應鏈佈局，除降低成本考量外，更以防供應鏈斷鏈危機。<br />\n<br />\n根據調查，諸多企業考慮把產能移向越南，不過，渣打專家認為，在這波全球供應鏈重組的過程中，台灣有效鞏固在其中的關鍵地位。<br />\n<br />\n渣打表示，全球經濟正面臨二戰以後最嚴重的衰退，預估2020年全球GDP成長率為-3.3％。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3334222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3334222&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7A5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=2055b837\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3334222&h=60ec43b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3334222</a>"},{"pid":"9b9b3278fae208f54e9e67af31955c8c169ad150","tid":2261262,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"台灣的機會來了"},{"pid":"f3132e4dff837d15bffad4d6cf065c1dc4ac9d7b","tid":2261262,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/24/Tvb_hail_commie_winner.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20181215123622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F24%2FTvb_hail_commie_winner.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F350%3Fcb%3D20181215123622&h=29c2ef13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a7829807391fe834c18bcce69972951de8d45ad","tid":2261262,"uid":152476,"li